1. Problem Definition

LLMs provide strong local reasoning but lack:
	‚Ä¢	persistent state
	‚Ä¢	identity-stable modules
	‚Ä¢	continuity across tasks
	‚Ä¢	governance constraints
	‚Ä¢	reusable internal architecture
	‚Ä¢	operator-specific coherence

PantheonOS solves these deficiencies through natural-language cognitive architecture ‚Äî a repeatable method of shaping model behavior into a modular operating system.

